🟢 1️⃣ ORM Concept

ORM = Object Relational Mapping

Meaning:

Java Object ↔ Database Table
Example:

Java class:

Student

Database table:

student

Mapping:

Java	Database
class	table
object	row
field	column

Example:

Java object:

new Student(1,"Hemanth","Spring")

Database row:

id | name    | course
1  | Hemanth | Spring


