# 2️⃣ Ippudu DB add chesinappudu

Flow ippudu ila undi:

```
Postman
   ↓
Controller
   ↓
Service
   ↓
Repository
   ↓
Hibernate
   ↓
MySQL
```

Ikkada Spring Boot **JSON body ni parse cheyyali**.

So server ki teliyali:

```
Request body format enti?
```

Example:

| Format    | Header                            |
| --------- | --------------------------------- |
| JSON      | application/json                  |
| Form data | application/x-www-form-urlencoded |
| File      | multipart/form-data               |

So server ki teliyali **JSON vastundi ani**.

