# 3️⃣ Content-Type header role

Example request:

```
POST /student/add
Content-Type: application/json
```

Body:

```json
{
"name":"Hemanth",
"course":"Spring Boot"
}
```

Spring Boot chustundi:

```
Content-Type = application/json
```

So Jackson use chesi:

```
JSON → Student object
```

convert chestundi.

---

# 4️⃣ Header lekapothe em jarugutundi?

Server confuse avutundi.

```
Body lo data undi
But format teliyadu
```

So error vastundi:

```
400 Bad Request
JSON parse error
```

