# 5️⃣ Why earlier automatic ga work ayyindi?

Postman **auto header add chesindi**.

When you select:

```
Body → raw → JSON
```

Postman internally add chestundi:

```
Content-Type: application/json
```

But konni sari:

```
Body type change ayina
or manual editing
```

appudu header remove avvachu.

Kabatti manam manually add chesam.

