# 6️⃣ Quick example

### Wrong request

```
POST /student/add
(no header)
```

Body:

```
{name:"Hemanth"}
```

Server:

```
Format teliyadu ❌
```

---

### Correct request

```
POST /student/add
Content-Type: application/json
```

Body:

```json
{
"name":"Hemanth",
"course":"Spring Boot"
}
```

Server:

```
JSON parse
Object create
DB insert
```

