# 7️⃣ Postman tabs explanation (short)

Response area lo nuvvu chusav:

| Tab          | Meaning            |
| ------------ | ------------------ |
| Pretty       | formatted response |
| Raw          | plain response     |
| Preview      | browser style      |
| Headers      | response headers   |
| Cookies      | cookies            |
| Test Results | scripts            |

